name: brooding
description:
"brooding" is the 6th song off my new beattape "souls" releaseing August 27, 2021. the song was made solely on my sp404 and my po33. its gritty, imperfect but also relaxing.  

the cover art was generated by AI using the text prompt "brooding souls." 

Bop your head and enjoy the music. If you purchase this piece, hit me up on twitter @ryanartwalker and I will send you the album with high quality AIFF files!
